Car Rental System

User will go to car reservation system.
choose location and he will get rental shops and he can choose vehicle on his preference date.
In rental store person can show booking document and take vehicle.
user can pay with card and upi
price will be charged on scooty base price + multiple by some number to get his value.


RentalSystem {
    rentalStores: List<RentalStore>,
    users: List<User>
}


RentalStore {
    vehicle: List<Vehicle>,
    reservations: HashMap<string, reservation>
}

Vehicle {
    id: string,
    name: string,
    isAvailable: boolean,

}

User {
id: string,
name: string
}
Reservation {
    id: string,
    rentalStore: id,
    vehicle: Vehicle,
    user: User,
    status: Enum("Confirmed", "Pending"),
    startDate: Date,
    endDate: Date,
    price: int
}

PaymentStrategy {

}

UpiPaymentStrategy{
}
CardPaymentStrategy{

}